ail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJb7UODv.jpg&h=4737ce7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"532c20807167541617f21e277f5d47e4050b3a8e","tid":2033791,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T09:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08410f9425e09825cbd1c684cb2492f169538ad2","tid":2033791,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T09:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2564ec63ac0b1eef332ea6048c916051a3619b86","tid":2033791,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T09:49:29.000Z","msg":"如果要真係建立一個香港軍團<br />\n一定要夠多香港人一齊參軍先得<br />\n以當年皇家香港軍團散解前既人數同埋而家啹喀兵既人數黎計<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>最終起碼要有3個Battalion, 姐係900-1000個香港人加入<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n聽落係好多，但係呢個已經比常規軍團既規模細<br />\n基本上無論係海外建軍或者東印度公司，1000人都係合理既數目<br />\n咁當然呢1000個人作為英軍聽命於英國，唔一定有機會打支那<br />\n但係將來退役之後可以為香港軍事上、政治上既貢獻一定會好大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有BNO，又覺得自己唔係好岩係外國讀書同做生意既巴絲，到時可以諗諗呢個方向<br />\n<br />\n[海外建軍另一出路?] 要求英國重組香港義勇軍團？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2076788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2076788</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓主請pin"},{"pid":"e53a4e82dfbf98049dbb43952a073c50ab44c73f","tid":2033791,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T09:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd45ccd56c7ec868461d496e0dd99e36697b24e5","tid":2033791,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T09:51:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef840614a6d1836d3140500c480f30f6c8e2aea","tid":2033791,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr